                <head>No. 706<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On October 5, a settlement of the Trieste dispute was reached when
                    representatives of Italy, the United Kingdom, the United States, and Yugoslavia
                    signed in London a memorandum of understanding and certain other agreements. For
                    text of the memorandum of understanding, see <ref target="#d293">Document
                        293</ref>.</p>
            </div>
